metadata.name: Up Til Now
metadata.description:
Up Til Now is a cumulative piece that is representative of the journey Kevin Maya has taken from the genesis of his career up until now. Included in the piece is 1,110 exclusive, never seen before images of exemplary, 21st-century tastemakers. From sacrifice and hardship to achievement and triumph this 1/1 piece is undoubtedly the only one of its kind. In the center of the piece lies an open space reserved for someone looking to cement themselves as part of history in their own right.
 
 **------------------------------------------------------------** 
 
 **Buying the NFT will additionally get you the following:** 
 
 **(1) You will receive a 1 on 1 photo shoot with Kevin Maya. Round trip airfare to LAX will be covered.** 
 
 **(2) You will receive original 6'x8' phyiscal piece.** 
 
 **(3) A photo of you taken by Kevin Maya will replace the center white square of the NFT.**
